None of that matters now, just grab
what you can and come with me.

492
00:30:49,900 --> 00:30:52,200
Aries 会派人跟踪我们
Aries will be sending men behind us.

493
00:30:52,800 --> 00:30:54,800
是什么让臂镯开始接通的？
What made the bracelet start broadcasting?

494
00:30:54,800 --> 00:30:57,200
我想不是我们造成的
I do not think it was anything we did.

495
00:30:57,200 --> 00:31:01,100
很可能是一种警报
就像飞船坠毁时会启动那样
It's possible it was like an emergency beacon
that activated when the dart crashed.

496
00:31:01,100 --> 00:31:04,500
从那以后电磁场的存在让它变得很安静
The EM field's been keeping it quiet ever since.

497
00:31:04,500 --> 00:31:08,700
但Mckay关掉电磁场的时候
它就开始传输信息
It must have begun transmitting
as soon as McKay turned off the field.

498
00:31:08,700 --> 00:31:11,600
听着，我们必须现在就走！
Listen to me.
We have to move on now!

499
00:31:11,600 --> 00:31:13,600
我们不能那样做
We cannot do that.

500
00:31:13,600 --> 00:31:18,100
Karris, 这很难解释，但我不如果不修好它就哪也不能去
-我们
- Karris, this is hard to explain,
but we can't go anywhere till we fix this device.
- We

501
00:31:18,100 --> 00:31:21,500
你们刚刚扔掉了飞船
如果留在这会有生命危险
You'll just have to abandon your ship.
You're risking your lives if you stay.

502
00:31:21,500 --> 00:31:23,800
这跟我们的飞船无关
This is not about our ship.

503
00:31:23,800 --> 00:31:26,500
这是关于你们村子的防御工事
This is about the protection of your villages.

504
00:31:26,500 --> 00:31:27,400
什么？
What?

505
00:31:27,400 --> 00:31:30,400
Karris, 我们飞船毁坏的原因
Karris, the reason our ship went down.

506
00:31:30,400 --> 00:31:34,600
和当年幽灵船坠毁的原因一样
都是这个装置引起的
The reason the Wraith dart crashed
so long ago, is because of this device.

507
00:31:34,600 --> 00:31:38,600
它屏蔽了所有依赖电磁场的技术
It renders all electro magnetic based
technology inside the shield, inert.

508
00:31:39,400 --> 00:31:40,400
我不明白
I don't understand.

509
00:31:40,400 --> 00:31:43,900
他们是说幽灵没有入侵
不是因为你们的祭祀
What they're saying is that the Wraith didn't
stay away because of your sacrifices.

510
00:31:43,900 --> 00:31:46,600
而是因为这个防御层
They stayed away because of this shield.

511
00:31:49,000 --> 00:31:49,800
这不是真的
That can't be true.

512
00:31:49,800 --> 00:31:53,100
这全部都是真的
防御层不能保护整个星球
It's not entirely true actually.
The shield doesn't protect the whole planet,

513
00:31:53,100 --> 00:31:55,800
它没有那么多能量
我相信祭祀的主意
it doesn't have enough power.
I believe the idea of the sacrifice,

514
00:31:55,800 --> 00:31:58,700
是让你们的种族不要远离
防御层的保护
was brought in so that your society
never left the confines of the shield.

515
00:31:59,200 --> 00:32:03,600
你瞧，祭祀对于你们的生存确实有重要的作用
但是不是你们所相信的那个原因
Look, the sacrifices play a part in your survival,
but not for the reasons you believe.

516
00:32:05,300 --> 00:32:06,500
不可能
That's impossible.

517
00:32:06,500 --> 00:32:11,600
我可以证明给你看
但你必须给我时间，让这个装置恢复正常
I can prove it to you. But you have to give us
time to bring this device back online.

518
00:32:14,200 --> 00:32:19,500
Karris很软弱
我怀疑他不敢献身
Karris is weak.
I doubt his oath to the sacrifice.

519
00:32:22,100 --> 00:32:25,100
那些成年人影响了他的判断力
The full growns have clouded his judgement.

520
00:32:33,100 --> 00:32:35,600
他们还在古迹那儿，并没有离开
They've stopped in the old city and are not moving on.

521
00:32:35,600 --> 00:32:37,100
拿起弓和箭
Get the bows and the spears.

522
00:32:37,100 --> 00:32:40,600
我们现在就把他们驱逐出去
永远不让他们回来
We will rid ourselves of them now,
once and for all!

523
00:32:43,800 --> 00:32:45,800
借过，借过，让一下
Coming through, coming through.
Excuse me.

524
00:32:48,100 --> 00:32:51,500
好吧，再让一下，谢谢
Alright.
And again, still in the way, thankyou.

525
00:32:54,900 --> 00:32:56,400
这肯定没什么用
This will never work.

526
00:32:56,400 --> 00:32:58,300
我们别无选择
We don't have much of a choice.

527
00:33:10,800 --> 00:33:13,400
Karris，这可不是大井
This is not the well, Karris

528
00:33:13,400 --> 00:33:15,900
我的错
It's my fault.

529
00:33:15,900 --> 00:33:20,400
我们刚刚得到McKay的消息
我们的飞船修好了
We just received word from McKay,
that our ship's just been repaired.

530
00:33:20,400 --> 00:33:23,900
事实上，他现在已经在飞船那儿等着我们了
In fact, he's back there right now,
waiting for us.

531
00:33:23,900 --> 00:33:27,300
我们刚刚在和Karris说再见
We were just saying goodbye to Karris.

532
00:33:29,100 --> 00:33:30,500
你觉得我是个傻子吗？
You think I am a fool?

533
00:33:30,500 --> 00:33:34,000
不，我只是觉得你有点猜疑
No. I just think you're a little cranky.

534
00:33:35,800 --> 00:33:40,100
看，如果你想让我们去飞船那儿
你可以看着我们离开
Look! If you want to escort us back to the ship,
you can watch us leave.

535
00:33:45,100 --> 00:33:46,700
带路
Lead the way.

536
00:34:24,800 --> 00:34:27,300
哦，你吓到我了
Oh, you scared me!

537
00:34:27,300 --> 00:34:29,200
是你吓到我们了
You scared us!

538
00:34:29,200 --> 00:34:30,900
- 对不起
- 没关系
- I'm sorry.
- That's ok.

539
00:34:30,900 --> 00:34:33,200
