We came to see if you left any chocolate.

540
00:34:33,200 --> 00:34:35,600
哦，当然留下了
Yes, yes, of course.

541
00:34:38,400 --> 00:34:39,800
什么？
What?

542
00:34:41,300 --> 00:34:44,300
哦，你们想要点巧克力
Oh, you want some.

543
00:34:45,100 --> 00:34:47,600
好，给你们这个
Ok, well you can have this,

544
00:34:47,600 --> 00:34:50,100
但你们要保证让我工作，好吗？
but you gotta promise to let me work ok?

545
00:34:50,100 --> 00:34:52,200
- 好
- 好的
- Ok.
- All right.

546
00:34:52,800 --> 00:34:54,500
安静点
Quietly.

547
00:35:06,300 --> 00:35:08,400
你想留McKay一个人在那儿吗？
Do you intend to leave McKay behind?

548
00:35:08,400 --> 00:35:12,500
我们在周围环绕飞行
直到他修好机器，他会来的
We'll circle around until he get's
the device back on. He'll show up.

549
00:35:18,200 --> 00:35:21,900
太晚了
我们太迟了
It's too late.
We're too late!

550
00:35:40,300 --> 00:35:41,400
那个鬼东西是什么？
What the hell was that?

551
00:35:41,400 --> 00:35:43,400
它太小，不可能是飞船
It was too small to be a dart.

552
00:35:43,400 --> 00:35:45,500
可能是某种探测器
It was a probe of some kind.

553
00:35:45,600 --> 00:35:48,700
也许是来检查一下幽灵臂镯发出的信号
Probably came to check out the signal
from the Wraith bracelet.

554
00:35:48,700 --> 00:35:51,500
在它回到星门前
我们要把它击落
We have to take it down before
it gets back to the gate.

555
00:35:58,800 --> 00:36:00,200
朋友们？
Boys?

556
00:36:03,900 --> 00:36:06,400
我们要把那个探测器击落
否则会有大麻烦
Let us take that probe down,
or we're all in deep trouble.

557
00:36:06,400 --> 00:36:09,900
即使你们能击落它
也会来更多的
Even if you were able to destroy it,
more will come

558
00:36:09,900 --> 00:36:11,700
不是这样的
That is not true

559
00:36:11,700 --> 00:36:14,300
Sheppard，你认为它们为什么会在这儿？
Why do you think they're here Sheppard?

560
00:36:14,300 --> 00:36:19,500
是因为你们，幽灵感觉到了猎物的存在
他们要来狩猎了
You. The Wraith have sensed a crop worth harvesting,
and they've come to claim it.

561
00:36:22,200 --> 00:36:28,200
Karris，你告诉他们，我们要把这个东西击落
在它飞回星门之前
Karris, tell them, that we gotta take this thing down,
before it get's back to the Stargate.

562
00:36:30,700 --> 00:36:32,500
还有一个成年人在哪里？
Where's the other full grown?

563
00:36:32,500 --> 00:36:33,800
Aries
Aries,

564
00:36:34,900 --> 00:36:38,400
有一个装置保护我们不受幽灵的袭击
there's a device that shields us
from the machines of the Wraith.

565
00:36:38,400 --> 00:36:40,800
- 祭祀很可能是……
