You have been protected from the Wraith,
by a shield.

569
00:36:49,700 --> 00:36:51,000
我们碰巧把它关闭了
We turned it off by accident.

570
00:36:51,000 --> 00:36:53,500
好消息是如果我们重新启动它
But the good news is,
that if we get it back up,

571
00:36:53,500 --> 00:36:55,600
幽灵就再也不会来了
the Wraith will never come again.

572
00:36:55,600 --> 00:36:58,900
只有一个方法可以确保幽灵不会再来
There's only one thing I have to do,
to make sure the Wraith never come again.

573
00:37:00,600 --> 00:37:02,200
就是杀死你
Kill you.

574
00:37:08,600 --> 00:37:09,900
帮帮忙
Come on.

575
00:37:19,700 --> 00:37:21,600
有人来了
Somebody is coming.

576
00:37:30,900 --> 00:37:32,200
这是什么？
What is this?

577
00:37:33,200 --> 00:37:35,700
- 你必须现在就跟我们走
- 我不能那样做
- You must come with us now!
-  I can't do that.

578
00:37:35,700 --> 00:37:39,100
听着，我需要在这儿完成我的工作
Listen!
I need to finish my work here.

579
00:37:39,100 --> 00:37:42,400
我见过幽灵侵犯别的星球
他们根本不在乎你们有多大
I've seen how the Wraith deal with other planets,
and they don't care how old you are.

580
00:37:42,400 --> 00:37:45,500
我要重新启动这个装置
很快就能完了
I need to get this device turned on,
and I am so close to figuring it out.

581
00:37:45,500 --> 00:37:47,300
给我一点时间吧
So just give me one more shot.

582
00:37:50,800 --> 00:37:53,800
听着，你们俩
回到你们的屋子里去
Look, both of you.
Go to your rooms!

583
00:37:55,300 --> 00:37:57,200
你们不听是吗？
You're not buying this are you?

584
00:38:04,500 --> 00:38:06,600
喂，嘘
过来，过来
Hey, psst.
Come on, come on.

585
00:38:12,500 --> 00:38:13,500
不
No.

586
00:38:16,700 --> 00:38:18,900
长官，我不希望变成这样
Sir.
I don't like where this is headed.

587
00:38:18,900 --> 00:38:20,900
没事的，Ford
Easy Ford.

588
00:38:24,300 --> 00:38:26,600
刚刚没人开枪
Nobody's shooting just yet.

589
00:38:27,800 --> 00:38:29,000
但是……
Yet...

590
00:38:29,000 --> 00:38:31,700
也没有人打算要开枪
And nobody's going to either.

591
00:38:31,700 --> 00:38:36,300
Aries, 你根本不知道你们要面临的是什么
Aries, you have no idea
what you're up against here.

592
00:38:36,300 --> 00:38:39,800
我们的武器比你们所见过的要先进很多
The weapons we carry are more powerful
than any you have ever seen.

593
00:38:39,800 --> 00:38:41,900
她说的是实话
She's telling the truth.

594
00:38:41,900 --> 00:38:45,500
它们不仅仅是只能发出大的响动
