- I must tell Aries. Come with us.

597
00:39:26,000 --> 00:39:28,100
嗨，你们还好吗？
Hey, you guys ok?

598
00:39:28,300 --> 00:39:30,600
回村子里去吧
就没事了
Head back to the village,
you're going to be fine.

599
00:39:37,300 --> 00:39:40,600
你们的存在引来了幽灵
Your presence has brought the Wraith.

600
00:39:40,600 --> 00:39:43,500
我们的先人祭祀
你们确破坏了这一切
All our ancestors sacrifices,
you've undone!

601
00:39:43,500 --> 00:39:45,900
这都是因为你们没按我们说的离开这
All because you refused to leave
when you were told to.

