00:39:45,900 --> 00:39:47,900
并不是那么简单
It's not that simple.

603
00:39:47,900 --> 00:39:50,000
就是那么简单
Yeah it is that simple

604
00:39:54,200 --> 00:39:57,800
- Aries, 不!
- Karris!
- Aries, no!
-  Karris!

605
00:39:59,600 --> 00:40:02,000
- 长官
- 别开枪
- Sir!
- Hold your fire!

606
00:40:03,700 --> 00:40:05,600
看看你做了什么
Look what you've done.

607
00:40:06,900 --> 00:40:09,000
他和你一样有罪
He's as guilty as you are.

608
00:40:11,100 --> 00:40:13,100
Ford?
Ford?

609
00:40:13,100 --> 00:40:14,500
准备好了，长官
Ready sir.

610
00:40:14,600 --> 00:40:17,300
我们要自卫了
We will defend ourselves.

611
00:40:17,300 --> 00:40:20,800
相信我，你们也不想那样
And believe me,
you don't want that.

612
00:40:22,300 --> 00:40:25,300
准备弓箭
Archers ready!

613
00:40:29,800 --> 00:40:31,300
它起作用了
It works!

614
00:40:31,300 --> 00:40:32,800
Aries!
Aries!

615
00:40:33,100 --> 00:40:34,400
