-  Aries! It works.

621
00:40:59,800 --> 00:41:01,500
你没事吧，McKay?
You alright McKay?

622
00:41:03,200 --> 00:41:05,100
我快喘不过气了
Gotta catch my breath.

623
00:41:11,300 --> 00:41:16,000
从飞船里拿药箱来
他会没事的
Get the medical kit from the jumper.
It'll be ok.

624
00:41:32,500 --> 00:41:37,100
如果没有能量增长的话
