- You'll have to get used to a few things,

632
00:41:58,600 --> 00:42:00,600
既然这儿所有的都改变了
now that everything's changing around here.

633
00:42:00,600 --> 00:42:03,300
但是我们下次来的时候可以讨论这个问题
But we can talk about that next time we visit.

634
00:42:03,300 --> 00:42:06,200
