637
00:42:10,300 --> 00:42:14,700
需要我们改变一些规矩
但是现在……是的
It will require us to change some laws,
but for now.... Yes.

638
00:42:17,200 --> 00:42:21,300
- 长官
- 这个给你
- Sir
- Oh right, here

639
00:42:21,900 --> 00:42:23,100
