Well where we're from, you get presents
when you turn a year older.

641
00:42:31,400 --> 00:42:33,300
盯着他，在那儿
See him, there.

642
00:42:33,300 --> 00:42:35,600
生日快乐
Happy birthday.

643
00:42:41,500 --> 00:42:43,100
你们去那儿吧
There you go

644
00:42:47,100 --> 00:42:48,700
给你一个


One for you.

